name: As Rich as Jeff Bezos
description: Jeff Bezos's estimated net worth at the time of minting is $202,000,000,000. The sales price of this NFT was calculated to account for 2.5% platform fees, a tax rate of 37% (the maximum for incomes above $523,600 for tax year 202﻿1), and the value of XTZ at the time of minting ($4.60).
